creator: Tozil
descriptionHtml:
You and your friends don't come up with funny and creative "Truth or Dare" tasks? Then this is the app you have to download.

This app contains:
+ more than 700 tasks (+ more coming up)
+ 4 selectable categories
+ the possibility to add your own tasks
+ the possibility to delete and manage the tasks
+ a darkmode
+ the language packages english and german

And best of all, the app is and will always be free to use! Though it will be updated and enhanced regularly.

Feel free to send feedback, suggestion for improvement, translation mistakes, bugs or new tasks to tobi.zillmann@gmail.com
